node.text: On the 20th Anniversary of 9/11 we vow to #NeverForget and to always #Honor911 @911memorial 🇺🇸🇺🇸 See how you can help at 911memorial.org

node.text: We will never forget ❤️🇺🇸 This year marks the 20th Anniversary of the 9/11 terrorist attacks. Tonight the iconic Tribute In Light will be shining from dusk until dawn. Learn more about the commemoration, Tribute in Light and how you can support the 9/11 Memorial & Museum at ➡️ @911memorial #NeverForget911#NYC
